  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The user holds his mirror against his targets, and fires a projectile made of light against him. The user makes a ranged attack roll at his maximum attack bonus for each shard. Said shard deal 1d4+1 points of slashing damage to the target; the user may target different creature for each shard, as long as they are within range. If the user creates more than 2 shards using this technique, he can shoot them against an Area 5-ft.-radius burst instead a target. Each shard deals 1d4+1, and reflex halves the damage.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Requires:</b> Mirror Arts (f)</p>\n<p><b>Material Focus:</b> One Mirror</p>\n<p><b>Empower:</b> The user can fire an additional sphere at the cost of 2 additional points of chakra (maximum 1 every 2 levels).</p>\n",
